<td style="border: 1px solid black; width: 20%;">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p>96.8</p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; background-color: #EEE; width: 20%;">Mind Affecting Resistance Scale (MARS)</td>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; width: 20%;">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p>8</p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; width: 15%; background-color: #DDD;"><strong>Personnel Notes</strong></td>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; width: 45%;" rowspan="3">Dr. Buchanan has a bit of a temper when work is slow, but he is dedicated to his work and very loyal to the Foundation. He has a knack for containment protocol—if you need something outside the box, he's the guy to call. Notably, he led the planning an executions for containing SCP-███, SCP-████, SCP-███ and SCP-████.</td>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; background-color: #EEE; width: 20%;">Ranser-G Ambition</td>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; width: 20%;">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p>77</p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; width: 15%; color: transparent;" rowspan="2">X</td>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; background-color: #EEE; width: 20%;">Burton-Hare Checklist</td>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; width: 20%;">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p>7</p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; background-color: #EEE; width: 20%;">SCP-2203</td>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; width: 20%;">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p>&quot;Burning&quot;</p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; width: 15%; background-color: #DDD;"><strong>Personnel Notes (Cont.)</strong></td>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; width: 85%;" colspan="4">
<p>I wish the man would stop nosing into containment files, though. We can’t wipe his memory (see below), so if this continues, we might have to do something about it before he gets himself killed.</p>
<p>CLEARANCE UPDATE ██/██/████: Granted Level 4 Clearance Access due to necessity for long-term containment planning as part of normal operations and duties.</p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; width: 15%; background-color: #DDD;"><strong>Medical Addenda</strong></td>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; width: 85%;" colspan="4">Dr. Buchanan has a severe allergy to most amnestics as well as SCP-148. Further research on this is pending.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: center; width: 100%; background-color: #BBB;" colspan="5"><strong>FOR OFFICE USE ONLY</strong></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; width: 15%; background-color: #BBB;"><strong>HIRE</strong></td>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; width: 85%;" colspan="4">██/██/███</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; width: 15%; background-color: #BBB;"><strong>TERMINATION</strong></td>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; width: 85%;" colspan="4"><span style="text-decoration: line-through;">██/██/███</span> SEE APPENDIX B</td>
</tr>
</table>
